CommentBody:
if its every job its possible this is weirdly caused do to a blocked install if they upgraded recently. 
I would pull a stock job from instant solutions and see if that one behaves the same way. If so reinstall the CU or update it.

- Migrated and upgraded to 11.5 from 11.0
- Hosts of group level throw error on all settings, but not job or global level
- Ran SQL script to update host name in SQL
- Ran robocopy script to copy over jobs
- Verified the host lists on the global level look normal

**Troubleshooting**
- Ran a repair on StealthAUDIT from P&F but did not correct our issue
- Collecting App logs and sql host script
